property="volumeNumber">37</span></span><span class="delimiter">, </span><span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationIssue">Number <span property="issueNumber">7</span></span></div><div class="doi"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.2017170050" property="sameAs">https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.2017170050</a></div></div><div class="info-panel"><div class="info-panel__left-content"><div class="info-panel__metrics info-panel__item"></div></div><div class="info-panel__right-content"><div class="info-panel__article_tools info-panel__item">



        
